OL,3,CNo conspiracy but 'systemic failures'
OL,4,Cin collapsed China spy case, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Systemic failures" rather than a
OL,8,Fconspiracy to sabotage the prosecution
OL,9,Fled to the collapse of a case against
OL,10,Ftwo alleged Chinese spies, a
OL,11,Fparliamentary inquiry has concluded.
OL,13,FIn a damning report, the Joint
OL,14,FCommittee on the National Security
OL,15,FStrategy (JCNSS) criticised both the
OL,16,FGovernment and the Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService (CPS) over a process beset by
OL,18,F"confusion and misaligned
OL,19,Fexpectations".
