OL,4,Cin collapsed China spy case, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAnd it cautioned against dismissing
OL,8,Fthe case as a "one-off" caused by
OL,9,Foutdated espionage laws, warning that
OL,10,Fthere are parallels in new legislation
OL,11,Fwhich must be handled carefully to
OL,12,Fprevent a similar issue from recurring.
OL,14,FFormer parliamentary researcher
OL,15,FChristopher Cash and Christopher Berry
OL,16,F` who both deny wrongdoing ` had been
OL,17,Faccused of passing secrets to Beijing
OL,18,Fbetween 2021 and 2023.
