OL,3,CNo conspiracy but 'systemic failures'
OL,4,Cin collapsed China spy case, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe cross-party group of MPs and peers
OL,8,Fsaid in a report on Wednesday: "We
OL,9,Fappreciate that the sequence of some
OL,10,Fevents has raised eyebrows.
OL,12,F"We did not find evidence of a co-
OL,13,Fordinated high-level effort to bring
OL,14,Fabout the collapse of the prosecution.
OL,16,F"Nor did we find evidence of
OL,17,Fdeliberate efforts to obstruct the
OL,18,Fprosecution, circumvent constitutional
OL,19,Fsafeguards or frustrate our inquiry."
