OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHowever, the committee added: "Overall
OL,8,Fit is clear that there were serious
OL,9,Fsystemic failures and deficiencies in
OL,10,Fcommunications, co-ordination and
OL,11,Fdecision-making.
OL,13,F"The Crown Prosecution Service could
OL,14,Fhave surfaced or escalated issues over
OL,15,Fmisaligned expectations much earlier.
OL,17,F"The Government team likewise did not
OL,18,Fhave sufficiently clear processes for
OL,19,Fescalating issues where there was a
OL,20,Flack of clarity."
