OL,3,CNo conspiracy but 'systemic failures'
OL,4,Cin collapsed China spy case, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIn its findings, the committee
OL,8,Facknowledged the CPS's assertion that
OL,9,Fit would have undermined the case at
OL,10,Ftrial if Mr Collins, the central
OL,11,Fexpert prosecution witness, refused to
OL,12,Fdescribe China as an active threat.
OL,14,FHowever, it said that taking the
OL,15,Fsenior official's statements together,
OL,16,F"in our view it is plain that... these
OL,17,Famounted to a more general active
OL,18,Fthreat to the United Kingdom's
OL,19,Fnational security".
