OL,7,FHe said the use of the term "enemy" in
OL,8,Fthe Official Secrets Act 1911 threw up
OL,9,Fdifficulties, which was replaced in
OL,10,Fthe National Security Act 2023 with a
OL,11,Frequirement for prosecutors to prove
OL,12,Fmerely that information had been
OL,13,F"passed to a foreign power".
OL,15,FThe JCNSS accepted the "root cause" of
OL,16,Fthe problems with the collapsed case
OL,17,Flay in the difficulties with the older
OL,18,Flaw, under which the charges had been
OL,19,Fbrought.
